{
  "chapter": 56,
  "chapter_summary": "陆小凤在幽灵山庄附近的浓雾山谷中迷路，循着烤兔肉的香气发现了一个神秘的栖身之地。他在沼泽边找到了烤肉的痕迹，却因误食含有大麻叶的兔肉而中毒瘫软。一个全身扭曲如蛇的畸形\"影子\"出现，此人自称曾是美男子，被老刀把子从百丈悬崖推下，在烂泥中泡了数十天后侥幸存活，靠沼泽霉菌和大麻叶维生。影子认出陆小凤，因见他未欺负阿雪而饶他一命。陆小凤通过推理揭穿影子就是叶雪和叶灵的父亲，影子恳求他不要告诉子女真相，宁死也不愿以这副模样面对他们。叶灵随后出现，识破陆小凤被点了穴道，先采来苦涩药草喂他服下，再将他抱往山洞。药草引发强烈的生理反应，叶灵趁机以身相许，坦言自己早已暗恋陆小凤，并因嫉妒姐姐叶雪而决心抢先。两人在山洞中发生关系，叶灵哭诉陆小凤\"欺负\"了她，随后破涕为笑，拉着他要\"回家\"，远方钟声响起，幽灵山庄仿佛又将有盛宴开始。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是陆小凤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "据说陆小凤是从来不会中毒的，现在怎么也中了毒？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "告诉你，这是大麻的叶子，我喜欢用它来烤肉吃，我吃了，就会觉得像神仙般快活，你吃了却会变得像条死狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "刚才你嗅到烤肉的时候，已经把它的毒吸进去一点，所以等到你再吃那块肉时，就绝不会有警觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你是故意引我来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那块肉却是我故意留下来的，否则就算是一匹马我也能吃下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你若找不到那块肉，我也许会放你走的，不幸你找到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "不幸？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我不能让任何人知道我在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你看见我了，你是不是觉得我很丑？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你若被人从几百丈高的山崖上推下来，又在烂泥里泡了几十天，你也会变成这个样子的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我以前非但不比你丑，而且还是个美男子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你被人从高崖上推下来，又在烂泥泡了几十天，可是你还没有死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我也不知道我怎么会活下来，就好像是老天在帮我的忙，可是老天又好像是在故意要我受折磨。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我就靠烂泥中一些还没有完全腐烂的东西填肚子，过了几十天之后才能爬出来，以后我才发觉，那些烂泥好像对我的伤很有用，所以每到我的伤又开始要流脓的时候，我就到烂泥里去泡一泡，这么多年来，居然成了习惯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是这种习惯实在不是人受的，幸好后来我又在无意中发现，大麻的叶子可以让我忘记很多痛苦，所以直到现在我还活着！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你知道我叫陆小凤，你认得我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不认得，可是我见过你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "几时见过的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "刚才。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你刚才见过我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知道了我的秘密，我本该杀了你灭口，就因为我刚才见过你，所以你还活着。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你总算还不是个坏人，并没有乘机欺负阿雪。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "阿雪一直是个乖孩子，我不要她被人欺负。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你是她的什么人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "西门吹雪为什么要杀你？你跟他有什么仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "他看见我跟他老婆睡在一张床上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我总算明白你是为什么到幽灵山庄来的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "我是为了避祸来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你也不怕死，你到这里来，只不过为了要发掘出这地方的秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "连阿雪那样的女人你都不动心，怎么会去偷西门吹雪的老婆？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "我只问你一句话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "我若是奸细，老刀把子怎么会让我活到现在，他是个多么厉害的角色，你总该知道得比我清楚。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你当然知道，因为从高崖上把你推下来的人就是他！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "但是你可以放心，我绝不会把这秘密说出去的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "因为我真的很喜欢叶雪，我绝不会害她的父亲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "谁是她的父亲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不错，我是的，大家都以为我已死了，连他们兄妹都以为我已死了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你至少应该让他们知道你还活着。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你千万不能告诉他们，千万不能。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我无论如何都不能让他们看见我现在这样子，我宁可也……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "千万不要说看见过我，我求求你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我刚才听见这里有人在说话，你在跟谁说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "跟我自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你几时变得喜欢自言自语的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "就在我发现朋友们都不太可靠的时候。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么要一个人躺在地上呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "因为我高兴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你自己点住自己的穴道，也是因为你高兴？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "这里的树叶和野菌大部分都有毒的，我无意中吃了一些，只好自己点住几处穴道，免得毒气攻心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "我点了自己的穴道后，才想到一个很严重的问题，因为我已没法子再将穴道解开，现在幸好你来了，真是谢天谢地。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "我知道你一定能替我把穴道解开的，你一向很有本事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你等一等，我马上回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你要我做的事，我全都答应，现在你能不能放我走？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我想看看阿灵究竟准备怎么样对付你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这小丫头从小是个鬼灵精，她玩的花样，有时连我都想不到。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "吃下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "你要我把这些乱七八糟的野草吃下去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这不是野草，这是救命的药，是我辛辛苦苦去替你采来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "要解开你的穴道很容易，可是你穴道解开了后，万一毒气攻心，我岂非反而害了你么？所以我一定要先替你找解药。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "现在我中的毒好像已解了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好像不行，要真的完全解了才行，反正这种药草对人只有好处，多吃一点也没关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "怎么样，好不好吃？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "唔，唔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这是什么声音？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "这是羊的声音，我忽然觉得自己好像变成一只羊。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我喜欢小绵羊，来，让我抱抱你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "你抱着我干什么？为什么还不把我穴道解开？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在解药的力量还没有分散，这里又不是久留之地，我只有先把你抱走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "抱我到哪儿去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然是个好地方，很好很好的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你的脸怎么红了？是不是在发烧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "看样子一定是那些药草的力量已发作了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "那些究竟是什么草？是救命的？还是要命的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是要命的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你是不是觉得很要命？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "简直他妈的要命极了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道有种药能把你治好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "什么药？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只有我能把你治好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "这是你自己找的，怪不得我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不怪你，你又能怎么样？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知不知道这种事有时候真会要命的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "你是不是一定要害死我？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我很想救你，我本来就喜欢你，只可惜……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我也是个处女，也从来没有男人碰过我。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "老实告诉你，你们在那里干什么，我全都看见了，看得清清楚楚。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "那是你姐姐……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她不是我姐姐，她是我天生的对头，只要是我喜欢的，她都要抢走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她明知道是我先看见你的，她也要抢，可是这一次我绝不让她了，你是我的，我要你嫁给我。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你要我嫁给你也行，无论你说什么我都答应。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你欺负我，你怎么能这样子欺负我？你害了我一辈子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你刚才答应过我的事，现在是不是就已经后悔了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你真的不后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling",
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "走，我们回家去。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling",
      "speaker_name": "叶灵",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "从今天起，你就是个有家室的男人，只要你不去找别的女人，我一定会像伺候皇帝一样伺候你。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 569,
      "line_end": 570
    }
  ],
